Yournoteof the 5this just received– It is too true that by the official returnsAllenbeatsCol Archerone vote–2There is a report to-day that there is a mistake in the return fromClay county, giving Allen sixty votes more than he really has; but this, I fear is itself a mistake–
               I have just examined the returns from thatcountyat the Secretarie’s office, and find that the agregate vote for Sheriff only falls short, by three votes, of the agregate, as reported, of Allen & Archer’s vote– Our friends, however, are hot on the track;
               and will probe the matter to the bottom–3
